    Get a dataset from the Open Government Data of Thailand API.

    th_get.Rd

    Get a dataset from the Open Government Data of Thailand API.

    Usage

    th_get(resource_id)

    Arguments

    resource_id

    Resource ID of the dataset to download.

    Examples

    th_get("245c98c3-2f92-4d58-a892-3fabf2af0772")
